summary: An ordinance relating to zoning and providing for the rezoning of Lots 9, 10, 11, 14, 15 and 16 of Block 20 and Lots 9 to 16 inclusive of Blocks 21 and 22, all in the Brooklyn Addition; with respect to Height District, and amending Ordinance No. 45382, as amended, by adding thereto one new section numbered 10-24.
